==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Roumanian
<hw>Rou*ma"ni*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An inhabitant of Roumania;
also, the language of Roumania, one of the Romance or Romanic languages
descended from Latin, but containing many words from other languages, as
Slavic, Turkish, and Greek.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>Rumanian</asp> and <asp>Romanian</asp>.]</altsp> ⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

